<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Mungu ulisema,
 Giza ilikoma;
 Twakushukuru!
 Twakusihi sote,
 Duniani mote
 Na kwa watu wote,
 Iwe nuru.

[V2]
 Yesu ulikuja,
 Ulituletea
 Nuru kuu;
 Macho kwa vipofu,
 Maisha kwa wafu;
 Twakushukuru.

[V3]
 Roho kiongozi,
 Roho wa mapenzi
 Tia nuru;
 Mwovu hata sasa
 Watu huwatosa,
 Tunakwomba hasa,
 Iwe nuru.

[V4]
 Mungu wa utatu
 Mwanga wao watu,
 Tuwe huru;
 Twende kote-kote
 Wafundishwe wote,
 Duniani mote,
 Iwe nuru.</lyrics>
<title>Mungu Ulisema TZR124</title>
<hymn_number>124</hymn_number>
</song>